<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Services — Gold Coast DJ Hire</title>
<meta name="description" content="Gold Coast DJ Hire services — weddings, corporate events, ceremony & cocktail hour, and private events across Gold Coast." />
<link rel="canonical" href="https://www.goldcoastdjhire.com.au/services.html" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../style.css" />
<style>
  .page-hero { padding: 10rem 2rem 5rem; background: var(--dark); text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .page-hero h1 { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; }
  .services-full { background: var(--black); }
  .service-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; padding: 4rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .service-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .service-row.reverse { direction: rtl; }
  .service-row.reverse > * { direction: ltr; }
  .service-img { aspect-ratio: 16/10; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; }
  .service-img-placeholder { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .service-content h2 { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-content p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .service-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .service-row.reverse { direction: ltr; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- MOBILE MENU OVERLAY -->
<div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
  <a href="/" onclick="closeMobile()">Home</a>
  <a href="/about" onclick="closeMobile()">About</a>
  <a href="/services" onclick="closeMobile()">Services</a>
  <a href="/blog" onclick="closeMobile()">Blog</a>
  <a href="/contact" class="mobile-cta" onclick="closeMobile()">Book Now</a>
  <a href="mailto:hello@goldcoastdjhire.com.au" class="mobile-email">hello@goldcoastdjhire.com.au</a>
</div>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><img src="../logo.svg" alt="Gold Coast DJ Hire" /></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
    <li class="nav-cta"><a href="/contact">Book Now</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Open menu"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
</nav>

<div class="page-hero">
  <p class="section-label">What We Offer</p>
  <h1>Services tailored <em class="grad-text">for you</em></h1>
</div>

<section class="services-full">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="service-row">
      <div class="service-img"><div class="service-img-placeholder">Corporate Events Photo</div></div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <p class="section-label">Corporate</p>
        <h2>Corporate <em class="grad-text">Events</em></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Polished, professional, and perfectly pitched. We set the right tone for product launches, galas, award nights, and company celebrations of any scale.</p>
        <a href="/corporate" class="btn-primary">View Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-row reverse">
      <div class="service-img" style="background:none;border:none;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?w=1200&q=80" alt="Wedding Reception DJ Gold Coast" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" /></div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <p class="section-label">Weddings</p>
        <h2>Wedding <em class="grad-text">Receptions</em></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>From the first dance to the last song, we curate a seamless musical journey that reflects your love story and keeps guests on the dance floor all night.</p>
        <a href="/wedding" class="btn-primary">View Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-row">
      <div class="service-img"><div class="service-img-placeholder">Ceremony & Cocktail Photo</div></div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <p class="section-label">Ceremony & Cocktail</p>
        <h2>Ceremony & <em class="grad-text">Cocktail Hour</em></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Subtle, elegant background music for ceremonies and cocktail hours — setting a warm, welcoming atmosphere before the evening begins.</p>
        <a href="/ceremony-cocktail" class="btn-primary">View Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-row reverse">
      <div class="service-img"><div class="service-img-placeholder">Private Events Photo</div></div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <p class="section-label">Private Events</p>
        <h2>Private <em class="grad-text">Events</em></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>From intimate private gatherings to exclusive celebrations, we bring the same professionalism and energy to every occasion — big or small.</p>
        <a href="/private" class="btn-primary">View Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <p>&copy; 2026 Gold Coast DJ Hire — All rights reserved.</p>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="mailto:hello@goldcoastdjhire.com.au">hello@goldcoastdjhire.com.au</a>
      <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
<div class="cookie-banner" id="cookieBanner">
  <p>We use cookies to analyse website traffic. See our <a href="mailto:hello@goldcoastdjhire.com.au">hello@goldcoastdjhire.com.au</a>
      <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
  <div class="cookie-buttons">
    <button class="btn-decline" onclick="declineCookies()">Decline</button>
    <button class="btn-accept" onclick="acceptCookies()">Accept</button>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
  window.addEventListener('load', () => { if (!localStorage.getItem('gc_cookie_consent')) setTimeout(() => document.getElementById('cookieBanner').classList.add('visible'), 1500); });
  function acceptCookies() { localStorage.setItem('gc_cookie_consent','accepted'); document.getElementById('cookieBanner').classList.remove('visible'); }
  function declineCookies() { localStorage.setItem('gc_cookie_consent','declined'); document.getElementById('cookieBanner').classList.remove('visible'); }
</script>
<script>
  const hamburger = document.getElementById('hamburger');
  const mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobileMenu');
  function closeMobile() {
    mobileMenu.classList.remove('open');
    mobileMenu.style.display = 'none';
    hamburger.classList.remove('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  }
  hamburger.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const isOpen = hamburger.classList.toggle('open');
    if (isOpen) {
      mobileMenu.style.display = 'flex';
      setTimeout(() => mobileMenu.classList.add('open'), 10);
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    } else { closeMobile(); }
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
